data.description: Home for the Holidays! Charming single family pool home located on a corner lot in the heart of Lancaster! Home features 4 good sized bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, open kitchen and dining area with indoor laundry & an attached 2 car garage. The back yard features a covered patio & inground pool, perfect for those warm summer days.
